Ah, this was fixed by PR #4793 (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/36ebbf1ddc3ed820b7a5572ff4ed8e9bc707b8e5)

Unfortunately, this fix didn't make it into the images for the latest release, I will look into that. 
In the mean time, an alternative would be to copy the latest files from 
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/models/rnn
into your own directory and run them.
